issue.title: Confusing!
issue.body:
It wasn't obvious to us that you need to have a tab opened on the 'slave' machine in order to see the files being viewed on the 'master' machine. We spent a while trying to configure things before we realised it this little gem works.

Recommend you update your readme to explain this caveat.

issue.title: Changes of one file show up in other
issue.body: I think there is some bug in this plugin which fails to differentiate between open files. Changes of one file show up in another.

issue.title: How to set to view only mode
issue.body: Can i to set only the master can edit the file, while others just look at it ?
